{"title":"windows下的go语言环境安装","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.033Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/windows下的go语言环境安装","updated":"2023-07-28T08:53:30.395Z","content":"<h2 id=\"windows下的go语言环境安装\">windows下的go语言环境安装<a title=\"#windows下的go语言环境安装\" href=\"#windows下的go语言环境安装\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>1、下载go语言的安装文件，<a href=\"https://golang.google.cn/dl/\" target=\"_blank\">点此下载</a>，仅需下载其中一个即可。这里我下的是zip包</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201116181802504.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p><strong>2、解压刚刚下载的压缩包包到本地文件夹，随便一个路径即可</strong><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201116182054592.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>3、在系统环境变量里面添加go语言运行的bin目录</strong></p>\n<p>进入我的电脑-&gt;右击选择属性-&gt;选择高级系统设置-&gt;选择高级栏目-&gt;点击环境变量-&gt;选择下方的Path-&gt;点击编辑<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020111618224345.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>点击新建-&gt;浏览查找的刚刚解压的go语言的bin目录-&gt;添加上去点击确定即可</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201116182313416.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n<strong>4、测试</strong></p>\n<p>新建一个文件夹-&gt;建一个test.go文件-&gt;用文本编辑器输入如下代码</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">package main</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">import &quot;fmt&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">func main() &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\tfmt.Println(&quot;Hello,World!&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020111618285330.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n在刚刚建的文件夹地址栏输入cmd，按回车<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020111618313086.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"><br>\n输入go的执行命令，按回车出现“Hello，World！”，安装完成。<br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201116183111607.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3UwMTQyOTI0MDI=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"windows下安装及配置Pycharm","link":"2023/07/28/windows下安装及配置Pycharm"},"next":{"title":"Windows安装Python环境","link":"2023/07/28/Windows安装Python环境"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/windows下的go语言环境安装/","toc":[{"id":"windows下的go语言环境安装","title":"windows下的go语言环境安装","index":"1"}],"reading_time":"442 字约 3 分钟"}